    "We provided a detailed explanation of how to place our findings in a statistical learning theory context.",
    "We do not claim that uniform generalization bounds are wrong or that any prior results are false.",
    "Instead, we show that the statements of theorems that fit our generic uniform template must be vacuous for the regimes where the models are able to fit a large fraction of random data.",
